### Mem0 OpenMemory API
### Base URL: http://localhost:8181

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8181
@userId = hackathon
@appName = openmemory

# ── MEMORIES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Add memory (infer: true — LLM extracts facts, date stripped — use only for timeless facts)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "text": "[session: 2026-02-25] I am using FastAPI as primary python framework for BE",
  "app": "{{appName}}"
}

###

### Add memory with date context (infer: false — stores as-is, date is searchable)
# Use this pattern when you want "what did I use in February?" to work.
# Include the date naturally in the text — it gets embedded and retrieved semantically.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "text": "On 2026-02-15 (February 2026 session): I am using FastAPI as primary python framework for BE",
  "app": "{{appName}}",
  "infer": false
}

###

### List memories (filter endpoint — GET /memories/ has upstream bug)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "page": 1,
  "size": 50
}

###

### Get single memory by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/MEMORY_ID_HERE

###

### Update memory
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/MEMORY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Updated memory content"
}

###

### Delete all memories for user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

# ── SEARCH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Search memories (semantic search via filter with query)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/memories/filter
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}",
  "query": "what project is Tomas working on",
  "page": 1,
  "size": 10
}

# ── CONFIG ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get full config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/config/

###

### Get LLM config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/config/mem0/llm

###

### Get embedder config
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/config/mem0/embedder

###

### Update LLM config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/config/mem0/llm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "openai",
  "config": {
    "model": "gemini-flash",
    "api_key": "dummy",
    "temperature": 0.1,
    "max_tokens": 2000
  }
}

# ── STATS & APPS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/stats/

###

### List apps
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/apps/

###

### Get memories for app
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/apps/{{appName}}/memories
